  <assign id="39">
    <name>Assignment #1: Use and Reflect on a Formative Assessment Technique</name>
    <intro>&lt;div&gt;Incorporate into your class one or more of the formative in-class assessment techniques shared in this course. Do it more than once so it becomes more than a novelty experience. Then, write a 2- to 3-paragraph reflection that describes the following:&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;What you did and in what setting (whole group, small, individual); How it was received by the students;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The information you learned from the experience;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;How you acted on that information;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Whether you would recommend the technique to a colleague; and&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Whether and how you would refine the technique for future use.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</intro>
